column1: Daily Weather Observations for Port Macquarie, New South Wales for August 2021
Prepared at 16:00 UTC on Saturday 16 October 2021   IDCJDW2197.202108
Observations prior to 15 October 2020 are available at Port Macquarie Airport (Comparison) {station number 060139}.
Some cloud observations are from automated equipment; these are somewhat different to those made by a human observer and may not appear every day.
Observations were drawn from Port Maquarie (Port Macquarie Airport Aw {station 060168}
